From e8bbe9ca937ccfa9f2bd3241125450ccfcd741c4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alexander Hoffman <alxhoff@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 19:01:10 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 10/11] media/i2c: Extend MAX9295/MAX9296 GMSL2 serdes for D4xx
 (JP7)

Serializer/deserializer support required by the D4xx driver, ported from
JP5 (0005/0010):

- max9296.c: pipe management (get/release/reset pipe, set_registers,
  init_settings, set_pipe), serdes lock/unlock, settings_setup guard,
  REGCACHE_NONE, src/dst pipe map registers
- max9295.c: per-instance prim_priv + sensor_regmap refactor (drop global
  prim_priv__), set_registers/init_settings/set_pipe, reset control
- headers: regmap-based sensor regmap init, lock/unlock_serdes prototypes,
  GMSL CSI data-type defines (YUV422_8, RGB_888, RAW_8)

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
